    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind some cosmetic and mechanical imperfections. The exterior shows its age with various scuffs, some fading paint on the hood, and a few minor dings. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs soon to keep it in reliable shape. It's a functional car that reflects its years of service.",
